{"tid":481081,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[匯豐+IT] HSBC / Microsoft Industrial Placement","createTime":"2017-11-26T19:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T11:38:32.000Z","uid":104684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"01153c042cc3b0f2f29d4a48274de3f2319b4fe6","tid":481081,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:51:04.000Z","msg":"The programme is 12-months in duration and commences in June 2018, with participants located in China (Guangzhou), Hong Kong and India (Pune &ndash; HSBC and Hyderabad &ndash; Microsoft).  The placement comprises of two, six-month rotations where you will gain solid AI experience from Microsoft and solve real business challenges, as well as engage in AI projects that will bring efficiencies to HSBC, and be at the forefront of AI showcases for the bank.<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nWorking at Microsoft<br />\n <br />\nThe placement at Microsoft will provide you exposure and hands-on experience in developing bots using recent Microsoft Artificial Intelligence technology. Your first month will comprise of extensive formal training in Hyderabad, India on Microsoft&rsquo;s campus, in areas such as big data and artificial intelligence technologies that will help you get started on your day-to-day work as well as projects.  After your training, you&rsquo;ll work on two projects: 1) optimising algorithmic trading, and 2) video analytics and computer vision.<br />\n <br />\nWorking at HSBC<br />\n <br />\nThe placement at HSBC will provide you exposure and hands-on experience in our Global Banking and Markets business, working with algorithmic trading technology. You will work with our traders and develop and support the algorithmic trading systems for Equities, providing low latency equity expertise.  You&rsquo;ll be trained in Unix, SQL, MongoDB, Python and algorithmic trading principles as part of your ongoing learning, along with other development opportunities.<br />\n <br />\n <br />\nApplications are currently open on close on Sunday 3 December 2017, with offers made to successful applicants in early February 2018.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hsbc.taleo.net/careersection/careersection/external/jobdetail.ftl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhsbc.taleo.net%2Fcareersection%2Fcareersection%2Fexternal%2Fjobdetail.ftl&d=xaBMCAPEdhMBgXjUKYuXTP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=03b9041f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hsbc.taleo.net/careersection/careersection/external/jobdetail.ftl</a>"},{"pid":"d5ccdd6a7776da54b883fc25d6493f121c96a38f","tid":481081,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T20:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315a03a2264decd0097befd8477a93b77fef5233","tid":481081,"uid":126736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T20:20:59.000Z","msg":"伏"},{"pid":"de1156d442daa4f04db59eecedbb797d8a9b7e76","tid":481081,"uid":98493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T20:23:27.000Z","msg":"報咗"},{"pid":"1d63bda2692079c9fee166655c6f12036dff2f74","tid":481081,"uid":80617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T23:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報咗</blockquote><br />\n巴打係master學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e968235b8d0f74a317a5d8dd125859a647aab55","tid":481081,"uid":1486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"點解條link死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f2fc18be9befeaec7ea1507a3888e9533d1c08","tid":481081,"uid":76358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"要返印度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc8587ea2484c41ad4e50683e66e59b1b9de577","tid":481081,"uid":98493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27